When you’re at home, the way you dress can set the tone of your entire day. As much as its super comfortable to stay in your pajamas all day, you should get up, dress up and get on with your day. The most important thing when dressing for working at home is comfort. Do make sure you’re comfortable. Here are some items to wear while you are working from home. Leggings  Tank top  Cozy jersey (when feeling cold)  Slippers  A tracksuit 